However, 蒋 is not a part of a native name for this person  and  Wikipedia policy is to confine foreign language material on English Wikipedia to bona fide "native names" for a subject. It is possible that 蒋 can be considered part of a native name for this person, but it needs to be demonstrated specifically that the 蒋 character is part of a native name.
